{"tha-ap145:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap145:0.2":"Chattavagga ","tha-ap145:0.3":"Vedikarakattheraapadana ","tha-ap145:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap145:1.2":"piyadassinaruttame; ","tha-ap145:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap145:1.4":"muttavedimakasaham. ","tha-ap145:2.1":"Manihi parivaretva, ","tha-ap145:2.2":"akasim vedimuttamam; ","tha-ap145:2.3":"Vedikaya maham katva, ","tha-ap145:2.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap145:3.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap145:3.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap145:3.3":"Mani dharenti akase, ","tha-ap145:3.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap145:4.1":"Solaseto kappasate, ","tha-ap145:4.2":"manippabhasanamaka; ","tha-ap145:4.3":"Chattimsasimsu rajano, ","tha-ap145:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap145:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap145:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap145:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap145:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma vedikarako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap145:7.1":"Vedikarakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}